<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ʿjybaⁿạ fy mḥbth ạlʿẓymẗ .. (yạ msyḥy)2
 qd ḥmlt ạlạ̹tẖm ʿn nfsy ạlạ̉tẖymẗ .. (tfdy rwḥy)2
 ạlqrạr- yạ ʿjybaⁿạ msẖyraⁿạ .. ạ̹lhaⁿạ qdyraⁿạ
 yạ ạ̉baⁿạ ạ̉bdyaⁿạ .. yạ rỷys ạlslạm .. yạ yswʿy
 2- yạ qwyaⁿạ qd gẖlbt ạlqbr wạlmwt .. (ḥyn qmt)2
 bl sḥqt ạlṣl wạlạ̉ʿdạʾ ạ̉sẖhrt .. (wạntṣrt)2
 3- yạ ḥbyby ḥbk yḥlw lrwḥy .. (fhw nwry)2
 bl sẖfạʾ wdwạʾ ljrwḥy .. (wsrwry)2</lyrics>
